entries.title_d: The Yacht made a stop in the Yavin system and met with a mercenary fighter. The computers indicate that some information was transfered between the two vessels and Command wants to know what that information contained.
entries.title: Yavin System: Inspect the Mercenary Spy
entries.split_quest_alert: Nice work, pilot. We are sending a freighter to your area for transfer of that data. Stand by for coordinates to the transfer vessel.
entries.quest_location_d: Command has a lock on the mercenary craft inside the Yavin system. You are to travel to the Yavin system and inspect the fighter. A navigation waypoint will be supplied to the mercenary spy's location.
entries.quest_inspect_d: Intercept the mercenary spy, disable his craft, and inspect it for the data that was transfered between the yacht and fighter.
entries.quest_dock_d: Once you have found the report, dock with the fighter, and transfer it to your craft.
